content: Yes, please draft the # Context portion swapping the new key you generated at the beginning of the session into the current key on this one. Feel free to incorporate the GCS info in there if you think that's how you would absorb it best. The other option is that I can leave it as an attachment and put into the current-execution-status folder. I'm not sure if it works better for you to have it all in one place in the PRR or if that would be too cluttered and confusing, so it's really up to you. Let's see the PRR that pulls it all together!
